content: The destination already contains files and folders with the same name.

comment.text: This translation key is used to display a message when a user attempts to add files or folders to a destination that already contains items with the same name. It appears in a conflict resolution dialog box, indicating that an overwrite option may be available.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'qovluqlar' is spelled incorrectly. The correct spelling is 'qovluclar'.

The translation '목표에 이미 같은 이름의 파일과 폴더가 있습니다' while generally accurate, doesn't perfectly convey the nuance of 'destination'. '목표' (target/goal) is a functional equivalent, but '대상' (dangsang) might be more appropriate to represent 'destination' in this context, referring to the place where files are being moved or copied.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider '대상에 이미 같은 이름의 파일과 폴더가 있습니다.' (Dangsange imi gateun ireumui failgwa folderga itseumnida.)

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'ບັນຈຸ' is not the most natural or common way to express 'contains' in this context. It sounds formal and a bit archaic.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider using 'ມີ' instead of 'ບັນຈຸ'.  A more natural phrasing might be: 'ຈຸດຫມາຍປັດຈຸບັນມີເອກະສານແລະໂຟນເດີທີ່ມີຊື່ດຽວກັນຢູ່ແລ້ວ.'

ai_spell_check_issues.description: While grammatically correct, the phrase 'ຈຸດຫມາຍປັດຈຸບັນມີແລ້ວ' can be slightly improved for flow. The 'ແລ້ວ' (already) feels a bit redundant after 'ມີ' (has).
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider removing 'ແລ້ວ' or rephrasing. For example: 'ຈຸດຫມາຍປັດຈຸບັນມີເອກະສານແລະໂຟນເດີທີ່ມີຊື່ດຽວກັນ.'

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'ෆෝල්ඩර' is a transliteration of 'folder' and while understandable, a more Sinhala equivalent might improve readability. 'ඡෙරිණයා' (cherinya) or a direct equivalent if one exists would be preferable.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ගමනාන්තයේ දැනටමත් එකම නමින් ගොනු සහ ඡෙරිණයා අඩංගු වේ.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: While understandable, the sentence structure 'ගමනාන්තයේ දැනටමත් එකම නමින් ගොනු සහ ෆෝල්ඩර අඩංගු වේ' could be slightly more natural in Sinhala. It implies 'files and folders contain'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ගමනාන්තයේ දැනටමත් එකම නමින් ගොනු සහ ෆෝල්ඩර ඇති.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'фолдере' is a slightly less common and less formal way to say 'folders'. While not strictly incorrect, 'фасцикле' would be a more professional and standard term in this context.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Одредиште већ садржи датотеке и фасцикле са истим именом.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'Hedef zaten aynı ada sahip dosyalar ve klasörler içeriyor' is a literal translation but could be more natural in Turkish. It implies the files and folders *currently* exist there. A better phrasing would emphasize they would cause a conflict.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Hedefte aynı isimde dosyalar veya klasörler zaten mevcut.
